#: tesys_tagboard/templates/pages/help.html:45
msgid ""
"The less than operator which indicates that returned posts will have a value "
"<em>less than</em> the token's value."
msgstr ""

#: tesys_tagboard/templates/pages/help.html:53
msgid ""
"The greater than operator which indicates that returned posts will have a "
"value <em>greater than</em> the token's value."
msgstr ""

#: tesys_tagboard/templates/pages/help.html:72
msgid ""
"Some search tokens may accept wildcards in the specified search value. These "
"will make the filter more permissive, allowing resulting posts that match "
"where the wildcard(s) may be replaced with any value."
